SOURCE:歓楽 += (100 * CX1 + (400 + (ABL:親密 * 10)) * CX2 + 100 * CX3)
SOURCE:欲情 += (MIN(ABL:親密 * 15,500) * CX1 + (300 + 50 * ABL:欲望) * CX2 + 150 * CX3)
