PALAM:欲情 += (SOURCE:情愛 + SOURCE:露出 + SOURCE:歓楽) * 3 / 2 + SOURCE:欲情 + SOURCE:苦痛 * 4 / 5 + SOURCE:快Ｂ * (2 + TALENT:Ｂ感度) * SOURCE_REVISION2(ABL:欲望) / 2000 + SOURCE:快Ｖ * (2 + TALENT:Ｖ感度) * SOURCE_REVISION1(ABL:Ｖ感覚) * SOURCE_REVISION2(ABL:欲望) * 9 / 10000
